People stuck with lower view counts on their IG Reels are usually making the same mistake: wrong audience, wrong message.

Here‚Äôs the fix I recommend to every client who wants to grow faster: the 3x3 hashtag strategy. 

- Use 1‚Äì3 hashtags about your ideal audience
- Use 1‚Äì3 about the solution you deliver
- Use 1‚Äì3 about the struggles your audience is actively facing

How to find the right hashtags:

Step 1: Search keywords your audience would use (not what you call yourself, but what they call themselves) and save the ones with 10K‚Äì500K posts.

Step 2: Look at hashtags your competitors or niche accounts are using and borrow the ones that are getting them engagement.

Step 3: Use Instagram‚Äôs ‚Äúrelated hashtags‚Äù feature: type your keyword in the search bar, scroll down, and pull 2‚Äì3 ideas from the suggestions list.

This method forces your content into the right conversations. It‚Äôs the difference between being ignored and being in demand.

#ContentCreators #InstagramGrowthTips #LowEngagement

This is not just a concept. It's a working system with real experience behind it. But it also raises new challenges around trust, reliability, and quality assurance.

What you‚Äôll gain from the session:
ÔøΩ A behind-the-scenes look at how AI agents are being applied in manual testing
ÔøΩ Lessons learned from building a virtual tester that interprets and runs natural-language test cases
